---
layout: base.njk
title: Notes
description: Short notes on what I'm thinking — observations, half-formed ideas, and things worth writing down.
permalink: /blog/
---
<div class="container">

  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="eyebrow">
      <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
      <span class="eyebrow-label">Blog</span>
      <span class="eyebrow-rule"></span>
    </div>
    <h1>Short notes on <em>what I'm thinking.</em></h1>
    <p>Observations, half-formed ideas, and things worth writing down.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="post-feed">
    {%- for post in collections.notes %}
      <article class="note">
        <aside class="note-meta">
          {% if post.data.tag %}<span class="tag">{{ post.data.tag }}</span>{% endif %}
          <span class="note-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</span>
        </aside>
        <div class="note-body">
          {% if post.data.title %}<h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>{% endif %}
          {{ post.templateContent | safe }}
        </div>
      </article>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>

</div>
